precis:
Regulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1114 - FOSETYL-
ALUMINUM) which establish maximum limits (MRLs) on residues of the
fungicide fosetyl-aluminum that can be detected on or in butterhead
and head lettuce and on a variety of imported vegetables.
